title: Mulan Dumpling, LLC, Recalls Frozen Meat and Poultry Dumpling Products Produced Without Benefit of Inspection
summary: EDITOR’S NOTE: July 27, 2023 - Details of this recall were updated to include an increase of 21,314 pounds to the original 1,560 pounds for a total of 22,874 pounds of product subject to recall. WASHINGTON, July 15, 2023 – Mulan Dumpling, LLC, a Hyattsville...
impacted_products: • 8-oz. plastic bag packages containing 10 pieces of “Mulan Dumpling Pork & Cabbage Dumplings”.
• 8-oz. plastic bag packages containing 10 pieces of “Mulan Dumpling Shrimp & Chives Dumplings” containing pork.
• 8-oz. plastic bag packages containing 10 pieces of “Mulan Dumpling Shrimp & Chives Dumplings” containing pork.
